This patch makes several improvements to the **Texture Packs** tab of the
PCSX2 Patch & Texture Manager.  It removes the misleading folder
icons, improves cover downloading, displays a placeholder when no
cover is available, and adds a search box with instant filtering to
improve the user experience.

