To apply this patch, save the above diff to a file (for example
`pcsx2_texture_tab_patch.diff`) and run the following command in your
repository root:

```bash
patch -p1 < pcsx2_texture_tab_patch.diff
```

After applying the patch, rebuild and run the application.  The
installed packs list will no longer display large folder icons, covers
will be fetched more reliably (including 3D art), a "No cover
available" placeholder will appear when appropriate, and you can
quickly filter the list using the new search box.  Column resizing,
alternating row colours and sorting have been enabled to improve
readability.